 Shoemaker Rigging would unload one cannabis machine and set in place;
 Shoemaker Rigging would rough level and remove all debris;
 Shoemaker Rigging has not included any utility disconnect or installation.

Move press brakes at your location in Kent, OH.
 Shoemaker Rigging would provide the equipment and labor for the above
referenced project;
 Shoemaker Rigging would move the old press brake outside;
 Shoemaker Rigging would move the new press brake in and rough level;
 Shoemaker Rigging has not included any utility disconnect or installation.

